# ─── LLM providers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The pipeline calls Claude in this priority order:
#
# TEXT prompts (profile extraction, scoring, resume tailoring):
#   1. claude CLI     — uses your Claude Code session, zero key needed
#   2. openclaw CLI   — uses your openclaw session, zero key needed
#   3. Anthropic SDK  — fallback if neither CLI is available (key required)
#
# VISION prompts (external form screenshot analysis):
#   1. Anthropic SDK  — ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#   2. Gemini API     — GEMINI_API_KEY
#   3. GitHub Copilot — GITHUB_TOKEN (requires active Copilot subscription)
#
# Uncomment whichever you have:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
